MyBot - Multifunctional Telegram Bot
Python Version
Aiogram Version
License

MyBot is a feature-rich Telegram bot with multiple interactive functions powered by OpenAI's ChatGPT API.

📌 Table of Contents
Features

Installation

Configuration

Usage

Project Structure

Contributing

License

✨ Features
AI Chat: Conversation with ChatGPT (/gpt)

Quiz Game: Interactive quizzes on various topics (/quiz)

Random Facts: Interesting fact generator (/random)

Character Chat: Talk with historical/popular figures (/talk)

Translation: Multi-language text translation (/translate)

Voice Interaction: Voice message processing (/voice)

🛠 Installation
Clone the repository:

bash
git clone https://github.com/MrJonson75/GPT_Telegramm_bot.git
cd mybot
Install dependencies:

bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
Install FFmpeg (for voice processing):

bash
# On Ubuntu/Debian
sudo apt install ffmpeg

# On MacOS
brew install ffmpeg
⚙ Configuration
Create .env file:

bash
cp .env.example .env
Edit .env with your credentials:

ini
TOKEN=your_telegram_bot_token
GPT_TOKEN=your_openai_api_key
PROXY=your_proxy_server_if_needed  # Optional
🚀 Usage
Start the bot:

bash
python app.py
Available Commands:
Command	Description
/start	Show main menu
/gpt	Chat with AI
/quiz	Start quiz game
/random	Get random fact
/talk	Talk with characters
/translate	Translate text
/voice	Voice interaction
📂 Project Structure
mybot/
├── .env.example            # Environment template
├── app.py                  # Main entry point
├── config.py               # Configuration handler
├── misc.py                 # Startup/shutdown handlers
├── handlers/               # Command handlers
│   ├── command.py          # /start command
│   ├── random_fact.py      # Random facts
│   ├── gpt_interface.py    # ChatGPT interface
│   ├── talk.py             # Character chats
│   ├── quiz.py             # Quiz game
│   ├── trans.py            # Translation
│   └── voice_gpt.py        # Voice processing
├── keyboards/              # Bot keyboards
│   └── keyboard.py         # Shared keyboards
├── resources/              # Resource files
│   ├── images/             # Image assets
│   ├── messages/           # Text messages
│   └── prompts/            # AI prompts
└── utils/                  # Utilities
    ├── chatgpt.py          # OpenAI wrapper
    ├── images.py           # Image handling
    └── voice.py            # Voice utilities
